<h2 class="govuk-heading-m govuk-!-margin-top-6">Analytics cookies (optional)</h2>
<p>With your permission, we use Google Analytics and Microsoft Clarity to collect data about how you use Find support for your family. This information helps us to improve our service.</p>
<p>Google and Microsoft are not allowed to use or share our analytics data with anyone.</p>
<p>Google Analytics and Microsoft Clarity collect and store anonymised data about:</p>
<ul class="govuk-list govuk-list--bullet">
    <li>how you got to the service</li>
    <li>the pages you visit in this service and how long you spend on them</li>
    <li>what you click on while you're visiting the service</li>
    <li>the first half of the postcodes you search with</li>
    <li>how you use Find support for your family</li>
</ul>

